data.description: Featuring three bedrooms, two full bathrooms upstairs and a basement with outside entry. Can be legal accessory apartment with proper permits. Step inside this charming abode and be captivated by its warm and inviting atmosphere. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living spaces, creating an ideal setting for both relaxation and entertaining. Natural light dances through the large windows, illuminating the interior with a soothing glow. The kitchen is a culinary haven with ample counter space. Whether preparing a quick meal or hosting a dinner party, this space is sure to inspire your inner chef. Adjacent to the kitchen, a cozy dining area awaits, perfect for hosting. The sprawling greenery and mature trees provide a sense of privacy, making it the perfect setting for outdoor activities or gatherings. Located in Port Jeff Station, you'll enjoy easy access to an array of amenities, including shopping centers, dining options, and recreational facilities. The nearby natural wonders, such as parks and hiking trails, invite you to explore and immerse yourself in the breathtaking surroundings. Embrace the opportunity to own this enchanting property.
